node.text:
In the high-flying modern era of professional surfing, it's very difficult to compete amongst the top tier of the CT without boasting an aggressive air game. Unless of course, your name is @connercoffin.
Follow Conner's rise to the #ripcurlwslfinals, link in bio. 🏆 @ripcurl_usa

After recently becoming the first woman to win a CT event at Barra De La Cruz, Mexico, @stephaniegilmore carved out a clear path to a record-breaking eighth World Title.
